# Timeline Interaction Patterns

Follow [ADR-004](docs/adr/004-timeline-interaction-patterns.md) for timeline UX:

- **No scrollbar** – Hide scrollbar on timeline; use CSS `scrollbar-width: none`
- **Drag to pan** – Click-and-drag on timeline to pan; use movement threshold to distinguish from row click
- **Scroll wheel zoom** – Ctrl + wheel cycles zoom level (month ↔ week ↔ day); plain wheel scrolls vertically
